{"tid":2327382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一年了，係邊個令你呢一年生活咁唔方便？","createTime":"2020-12-16T04:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T04:59:22.000Z","uid":21255,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69ca7e0c011d43bc4d729a8c6f6232ac568d4907","tid":2327382,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:37:41.000Z","msg":"係中國人，<br />\n自私基因帶毒四圍傳播<br />\n封鎖消息令疫症不可收拾<br />\n吹噓防控令民眾錯估形勢<br />\n<br />\n係港共政府，<br />\n防疫政策不理民眾地離地<br />\n封關一拖再拖<br />\n相反台灣而家出街唔洗戴口罩<br />\n經濟正增長<br />\n<br />\n生生世世都不要忘記我們的仇人是誰<br />\n是誰害到我地咁撚慘<br />\n係香港拍拖都拍到long D 咁<br />\n大學生活對住個mon<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母啊中國人"},{"pid":"4c37312c1fe983c9211648a3616a15514754faa4","tid":2327382,"uid":327169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">林鄭月娥</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb2b9245e7e6ad9da3904fbc4b4635003198373","tid":2327382,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"似乎外國左膠共諜唔撚認同<br />\n最衰都係侵侵"},{"pid":"59371db6476e0d5982ac5abaa7a2a7dbc6d8e1e4","tid":2327382,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E4%BD%95%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%80-20200305115226_52cf_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%2580-20200305115226_52cf_large.jpg&h=afe5e8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"h